@startuml
skinparam BackgroundColor white
title Обзор runtime-взаимодействий
actor User
participant Telegram
participant "Бот (Micronaut)" as Bot
participant "Queue API\n(Orchestra/Axioma)" as Queue
participant "CometD/Kafka" as Events
User -> Telegram: /start + выбор услуги
Telegram -> Bot: update (long polling)
Bot -> Queue: GET services / POST visit
Queue --> Bot: данные талона
Bot --> Telegram: номер талона
Events -> Bot: VISIT_CALL / VISIT_RECALL
Bot --> Telegram: уведомление о вызове
@enduml
